# Privacy Policy for FollowUp+

Effective Date: [09/06/2025]

FollowUp+ ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our app handles your data.

## Information We Collect

FollowUp+ does **not** collect or share personal information from your device. All data remains local on your phone and is never sent to external servers.

Specifically:
- We store templates, contact numbers, and tags **only on your device**.
- No analytics, tracking, or ads collect personal data.
- The app accesses call state and phone number **only for the purpose of creating reminders or sending messages** â€” no data is stored externally.

## Permissions Used

- **Phone State**: To detect when a call ends and prompt for a follow-up message.
- **Contacts (optional)**: To personalize message templates with contact names.
- **Camera (optional)**: If enabled, used only for scanning phone numbers and initiating follow-ups.

## Data Retention

Since we do not collect or store any user data externally, there's nothing retained or shared.

## Third Parties

We do not share data with any third-party service providers.

## Your Consent

By using FollowUp+, you consent to this privacy policy.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy in the future. Any changes will be posted here.

## Contact

If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us at: [followupapps@outlook.com]
